title.narrative: Support for Service Delivery Integration-Services (SSDI-Services) Project

description.narrative: Designed to help the country successfully reduce fertility and population growth, lower the risk of HIV and reduce maternal, infant and under-five mortality rates, the project focuses on scaling up access and quality of an essential package of health services at facilities and mobilizing communities to utilize these services.
